description: Product Description Pampers Sensitive Baby Wipes Wipes 4 Packaging = 208. Your baby's sensitive skin deserves the familiar skin protection Pampers. Pampers Sensitive baby wipes are clinically tested milder than cleaning with cotton and water. The unique pH balanced formula Pampers helps prevent skin irritation because the natural pH of the skin preserves. And because they are designed specifically for sensitive skin of your baby, Pampers Sensitive baby wipes contain no perfume or alcohol. Pampers Sensitive baby wipes are dermatologically tested and suitable for use from birth Ingredients Aqua, Citric Acid, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Sodium Citrate, Sorbitan Caprylate, Sodium Benzoate, Disodium EDTA, Bis-PEG / PPG-16/16 PEG / PPG-16/16 Dimethicone, Xanthan Gum, Pentadecalactone, Dipropylene Glycol, Caprylic / Capric Triglyceride Directions Use the wipe to gently clean your baby's skin. Safety Warning To avoid danger of suffocation and/or strangulation, keep all packaging material away from babies and children.
